CHANGES
=======

0.1.0 (Unreleased)
------------------

* Initial project specification and documentation
* Added README.md with project overview
* Added QUICKSTART.md with getting started guide
* Added ARCHITECTURE.md with system design
* Added DESIGN.md with design decisions and rationale
* Added CONTRIBUTING.md with contribution guidelines
* Added API.md with library API reference
* Added dual MIT/GPL-3.0 license
* Set up pbr for build and version management
* Set up Pipenv for dependency management
* Implemented the complete ``cascconf`` Python package:

  * ``cascconf.api`` — ``merge_configs()`` public entry point
  * ``cascconf.cli`` — ``argparse``-based CLI (``cascconf`` command)
  * ``cascconf.discovery`` — ``DiscoveryConfig`` and directory scanner
  * ``cascconf.merger`` — deep and shallow merge strategies
  * ``cascconf.parser`` — extension-based format detection with fallback chain
  * ``cascconf.registry`` — pluggable parser/writer registry
  * ``cascconf.writer`` — serialise to JSON, YAML, or TOML
  * ``cascconf.exceptions`` — typed exception hierarchy
  * ``cascconf.__main__`` — ``python -m cascconf`` support
  * ``py.typed`` marker for PEP 561 inline type information

* Added 99 unit tests across 7 test modules; coverage threshold set to 90%
* Added test fixtures for base, override, and extra merge scenarios
* Made ``pyyaml`` and ``tomli-w``/``tomli`` optional package extras (``cascconf[yaml]`` and ``cascconf[toml]``)
* Removed ``validate_config`` to simplify the public API
* Simplified the parser: removed internal ``run()`` helper
* Updated API.md to reflect the simplified interfaces
* Fixed dev workflow: aligned Pipfile scripts and CONTRIBUTING.md to use ``pipenv run`` consistently
* Removed ``python_version`` from Pipfile ``[requires]`` (redundant with ``requires-python`` in ``pyproject.toml``)
* Increased maximum line length to 127 characters (black, isort, flake8)
* Applied ``black`` and ``isort`` formatting at the new line length
* Fixed all flake8 linting issues (E721 type comparison, F401/F811 unused imports)
* Fixed all mypy type-checking issues (missing stubs, stale ``type: ignore`` comments, ``no-any-return``, ``arg-type``)
